  <entry>
    <title>picgo配置</title>
    <link href="/2022/04/20/picgo%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <url>/2022/04/20/picgo%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Picgo配置"><a href="#Picgo配置" class="headerlink" title="Picgo配置"></a>Picgo配置</h2><ul><li>设置仓库名：<code>用户名/仓库名</code></li><li>设置分支名：之前默认是<code>master</code>，现在是<code>main</code></li><li>设置Token：就是刚刚复制的那一段令牌密令</li><li>下面两个非必填</li></ul><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tsunho12/photos_library/img/20220414204619.png" alt="Picgo设置"></p><h2 id="VsCode配置"><a href="#VsCode配置" class="headerlink" title="VsCode配置"></a>VsCode配置</h2><p>如同Picgo设置一样<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tsunho12/photos_library/img/20220414204708.png" alt="VsCode设置"></p><h2 id="Jsdelivr-cdn加速"><a href="#Jsdelivr-cdn加速" class="headerlink" title="Jsdelivr cdn加速"></a>Jsdelivr cdn加速</h2><p>默认使用github的链接有时候不稳定<br><code>https://raw.githubsercontent.com/用户名/仓库名/分支</code><br>下面我们该成cdn加速<br><code>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/GitHub用户名/仓库名</code></p><h2 id="Picgo快捷方式"><a href="#Picgo快捷方式" class="headerlink" title="Picgo快捷方式"></a>Picgo快捷方式</h2><ul><li>从剪切板上传图片到图床</li><li>Windows&#x2F;Unix: <code>Ctrl + Alt + u</code></li><li>macOS: <code>Cmd + Opt + u</code></li></ul><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tsunho12/photos_library/img/20220414204956.png" alt="gif演示"></p><ul><li>从文件夹上传图片到图床</li><li>Windows&#x2F;Unix: <code>Ctrl + Alt + e</code></li><li>macOS: <code>Cmd + Opt + e</code></li></ul><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tsunho12/photos_library/img/20220414205101.png" alt="gif演示"></p><ul><li>从输入框中输入图片名称上传到图床</li><li>Windows&#x2F;Unix: <code>Ctrl + Alt + o</code></li><li>macOS: <code>Cmd + Opt + o</code></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    <categories>
      
      <category>picgo</category>
      
